item.title: I already have JDK!Why does it say i need it?!?!
item.dc:creator: @Bloodcompany Bloodcompany
item.description:
@Bloodcompany wrote:

go to:
C:\Program Files\Java
check ur jdk version (ex jdk1.6.0_03)
make a new batch file and make the code like this:

"C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.6.0_03/bin/javac" *.java
pause

change the jdk1.6.0_03 to your own version
